00:55:47.980 --> 00:55:49.800
So as a result of Baccarum,

00:55:51.101 --> 00:55:53.021
we should recognize that life

00:55:54.016 --> 00:55:55.177
is a test for all of us,

00:55:55.916 --> 00:55:58.438
an opportunity for us to prove ourselves

00:55:58.458 --> 00:55:58.918
to God.

00:55:59.659 --> 00:56:01.440
And even though he isn't expecting a whole

00:56:01.480 --> 00:56:02.239
lot from us,

00:56:02.780 --> 00:56:04.922
fewer than one in a million pass muster.

00:56:06.101 --> 00:56:09.583
To earn Yahowah's trust and to be included

00:56:09.643 --> 00:56:10.864
among the Bachar,

00:56:11.786 --> 00:56:13.326
the chosen and tested ones,

00:56:14.646 --> 00:56:15.947
we must be observant,

00:56:17.288 --> 00:56:18.509
we must be responsive,

00:56:19.128 --> 00:56:20.230
and we must be reliable.

00:56:21.536 --> 00:56:24.137
And I would define observant the way that

00:56:24.478 --> 00:56:26.820
I translate Shamar.

00:56:28.422 --> 00:56:33.686
Closely examine and carefully consider.

00:56:33.786 --> 00:56:36.070
And then what you find is that when

00:56:36.090 --> 00:56:38.592
Yahowah is describing all of this,

00:56:39.793 --> 00:56:40.514
he will tell us,

00:56:42.690 --> 00:56:43.590
Through oath,

00:56:43.632 --> 00:56:45.391
you remember that word oath that I brought

00:56:45.411 --> 00:56:47.414
up so many times where we're told that

00:56:47.434 --> 00:56:50.815
the greater and lesser luminaries serve as

00:56:50.934 --> 00:56:55.257
an oath to the Mowedym,

00:56:55.297 --> 00:56:58.980
these restoring witnesses to the eternal

00:56:59.019 --> 00:57:01.141
testimony that are the seven appointments

00:57:01.161 --> 00:57:01.860
with Yahyachir.

00:57:02.541 --> 00:57:04.722
And it's rendered in English Bibles

00:57:05.003 --> 00:57:07.083
deduced to nothing but sign.

00:57:08.784 --> 00:57:10.365
Now that's not its verbal root.

00:57:14.304 --> 00:57:17.806
Its verbal root is written the same way

00:57:17.887 --> 00:57:18.606
in the Hebrew.

00:57:20.389 --> 00:57:23.891
And it means to be willing,

00:57:25.152 --> 00:57:29.815
to be responsive, to consent,

00:57:30.797 --> 00:57:34.440
to have been asked to do something and

00:57:34.480 --> 00:57:39.164
to show a willingness to get it done.

00:57:39.204 --> 00:57:41.806
That's what the oath actually are.

00:57:43.429 --> 00:57:44.769
They are the responsive ones.

00:57:47.050 --> 00:57:48.690
We get right back to it all over

00:57:48.751 --> 00:57:49.052
again.

00:57:50.771 --> 00:57:54.112
The qualification for working with Yahowah

00:57:55.632 --> 00:57:56.534
is responding to it.

00:58:01.715 --> 00:58:05.396
So there are chosen and tested ones that

00:58:06.036 --> 00:58:09.056
are observant, responsive and reliable.

00:58:10.170 --> 00:58:12.032
at least to the extent God is comfortable

00:58:12.072 --> 00:58:15.532
with us accompanying him into the fourth,

00:58:15.572 --> 00:58:17.034
fifth, sixth and seventh dimension.

00:58:17.434 --> 00:58:19.735
We have to demonstrate that we are

00:58:19.775 --> 00:58:20.375
observant,

00:58:20.894 --> 00:58:24.436
responsive and reliable to the extent that

00:58:24.476 --> 00:58:25.556
God says, yep,

00:58:25.996 --> 00:58:29.217
I am willing to empower this soul knowing

00:58:29.257 --> 00:58:31.798
