00:58:31.838 --> 00:58:34.340
I'm going to give them access to the

00:58:34.400 --> 00:58:37.681
entire universe and access to come into

00:58:37.722 --> 00:58:38.402
Shamaym

00:58:39.648 --> 00:58:43.211
and to be part of my family,

00:58:43.771 --> 00:58:46.574
communicating with me and all of the other

00:58:46.614 --> 00:58:48.297
covenant members forever.

00:58:49.157 --> 00:58:51.159
For him to make that call and to

00:58:51.239 --> 00:58:53.581
say yes to that, you don't,

00:58:54.141 --> 00:58:56.063
there is no secret little formula where

00:58:56.083 --> 00:58:56.885
you can say, okay,

00:58:56.965 --> 00:58:58.346
I'll accept the five conditions of the

00:58:58.385 --> 00:58:58.686
covenant.

00:58:58.706 --> 00:58:59.887
I'll attend the Mow'ed McRae.

00:58:59.967 --> 00:59:00.547
I'm in, right?

00:59:00.969 --> 00:59:02.891
No, you're not in.

00:59:04.565 --> 00:59:06.344
You have to continue to be observant,

00:59:06.364 --> 00:59:08.786
which means closely examine and carefully

00:59:08.846 --> 00:59:18.088
consider, responsive and reliable.

00:59:18.208 --> 00:59:22.608
In this regard, we are being Basar,

00:59:23.969 --> 00:59:26.730
examined and approved, right here,

00:59:27.230 --> 00:59:30.510
right now, scrutinized and verified,

00:59:32.050 --> 00:59:33.891
and the process of being found acceptable,

00:59:35.309 --> 00:59:35.990
and desirable.

00:59:37.411 --> 00:59:41.235
It is an open invitation with your life

00:59:41.375 --> 00:59:46.818
